The Chronicle Business Reporter
SCHWEPPES Zimbabwe Limited chief executive officer, Mr Charles Msipa, has been appointed to the board of FBC Holdings Limited. Mr Msipa is a renowned industrialist and past president of the Confederation of Zimbabwe Industries (CZI). His appointment was made during the recent FBC group’s 6th Annual General Meeting held in Harare. In a notice on the results of the AGM, FBC Holdings indicated that the appointment of Mr Msipa to the group’s board was among the resolutions shareholders approved.